,"tag-miserliness-al-bukhl","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-punishment-al-uqubah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4sv","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26759,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/15\/spend-sadaqah-not-bakhil\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Spend in charity, do not be miserly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Asma\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpend in charity and do not count it, lest Allah count it against you. Do not hoard it, lest Allah withhold from you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2451, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1029 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19201,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/19\/oath-by-allah-charity-patience\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Character: I swear by Allah on three qualities","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Kabshah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI swear an oath by Allah on three qualities and I will tell you about them, so memorize them: the wealth of a servant is not decreased by charity, a servant is not wronged by oppression\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40002,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/11\/way-of-allah-multiplied\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Spending in the way of Allah multiplied","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Khuraym ibn Fatik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever donates charity in the way of Allah, it will be multiplied up to seven hundred times in his record.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1625 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u062e\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/21\/give-sadaqah-even-small\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Give whatever you can in charity, even small","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Bujayd reported: She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the poor come to my door and I cannot find anything to give them.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you can find nothing but a burnt trotter, hand it over to them.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18055,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/zakat-allah-withholds-rain\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Zakat: Rain held back if people withhold charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNever do people withhold alms from their wealth but that a portion from the sky will be held back; were it not for the animals, it would never rain.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 13454 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24126,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/05\/charity-like-emancipation\/","url_meta":{"origin":17143,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Giving in charity like freeing slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn 'Azib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever donates a gift of milk, or a piece of silver, or who guides others through a strait, he will be rewarded as if he has freed a slave.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1957 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v